<body lang=3D"EN-US" link=3D"#467886" vlink=3D"#96607D" style=3D"word-wrap:=
break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Good afternoon Rafaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">I wanted to take the time to thank you very much for meeting with Chri=
s, David and myself at your place this afternoon. It was much appreciated.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">I felt that the meeting was very productive and positive as we all dis=
cussed the next steps and have agreed on the claim&#8217;s progression proc=
ess moving forward.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">I would like to re-confirm the next steps we agreed to in writing, and=
 share with all as below:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0in" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 =
lfo1"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">Asset Restor=
e to attend site as soon as possible and complete the process of assessing =
and cataloging the contents for the response of
 the contents claim. After assessment the contents which are categorised as=
 a total loss will be removed from site.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D=
"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span =
style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">Asset Restore to strip o=
ut the property of any fire or smoke damaged linings or other non-structura=
l items. This will enable a clear and
 clean structural assessment to be undertaken, from which we will produce a=
 scope of works for the repairs required.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=
=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><sp=
an style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif">Once we have a scope =
of works completed &#8211; we will share this with you to approve before we=
 submit to our repair panel for tendering.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Confirming that you have notified us of the access code to be 1106.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">We will keep you updated on the above process and communicate with you=
 as we move through the above steps.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">I have spoken with both our Motor and our Claims Team Leaders, and the=
y have said that the items you have enquired about are very unlikely to be =
affected by the fire given their location with
 respect to the proximity of the fire. I do understand that you would like =
to be 100% certain that the lithium batteries in these items have not been =
affected from the fire. The standard process in this situation is that you =
can undertake any testing of any
 of your items which you wish to, to obtain test results or a report which =
your insurer can consider for inclusion in your claims. If the test results=
 prove any damage or loss to these items from the fire &#8211; then your in=
surer will consider them within your claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">For contents items - please direct your enquiries to
<a href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz">claims@tower.co.nz</a><o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">As you do not yet have a motor claim with Tower from this event &#8211=
; you can also send any motor reports to
<a href=3D"mailto:claims@tower.co.nz">claims@tower.co.nz</a> and they will =
respond accordingly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Thank you again and I strongly encourage you to call me on the number =
below with any concerns that you have with the process of the claim progres=
sion.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">All the best,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Grant. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
